OUR PRIVACY MISSION STATEMENT
Effective: July 1, 2023
We recognize that when our customers, partners, prospective clients, and other individuals provide personal data to
OVH US LLC dba OVHcloud
®
("
OVHcloud
"), they trust that we will respect their privacy.
We don't take that trust lightly and have committed to taking measures to safeguard each individual's privacy and protect the personal data we handle.
We strive to be transparent with you about the data we collect about you and how it is used and shared. In turn, we believe that you should have choices regarding how we obtain, collect, share, and utilize your personal data.
Here is a detailed look into these promises.
Privacy Policy
