to give you access to specific functionalities and to recognise you
, to indicate that you have passed through one of the pages and to improve your browsing comfort by adapting the presentation according to your display preferences on your terminal, to memorise passwords or any information relating to a form you have filled in on the Site or Application.
Analytics and audience measurement:
These cookies, issued by us or our technical service providers, enable statistical analyses to be made of the browsing habits of Users of the Site and the Application. The results of these analyses
are processed anonymously and for statistical purposes
only. In addition to analysing the number of visitors, they make it possible, where necessary, to detect browsing problems and, consequently, to improve the ergonomics of our Services. The traffic analysis services used by the Site and the Application only produce and send to our technical service providers aggregated statistics and traffic volumes. The lifetime of these cookies is thirteen (13) months. We also use tools to measure the effectiveness of our email campaigns, enabling us to take relevant commercial action based on the information collected.
